                     <interp inst="t18050918-17-off82" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050918-17-off82" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050918-17-cd83" type="crimeDate">7th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050918-17-off82 t18050918-17-cd83"></join>, a man's hat, value 6 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18050918-17-victim179" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Spyley
                        <interp inst="t18050918-17-victim179" type="surname" value="Spyley"></interp>
